UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 905
1 (1) As used in this section, "Green Star flag" means a flag with a green star
2 prominently displayed in the center of a white background and surrounded by a
3 red border.
4 (2) The Green Star flag is designated as the Commonwealth's symbol of continued
5 awareness of military service member and veteran suicide and the commitment to
6 recognize and resolve military service member and veteran suicide.
7 (3) All Green Star flags purchased by a public institution or displayed by a public
8 institution shall be manufactured in the United States.
9 (4) The Green Star flag may be displayed wherever there is a flag of the United
10 States, Commonwealth of Kentucky flag, or POW/MIA flag.
